Blocks Buster :Color Fill 3D - Fill Line Colour 3D

The best game to kill the time


"Blocks Buster :Color Fill 3D" is a 3D style block game. It is classic and fun. "Blocks Buster :Color Fill 3D" is addictive because of the block pop rules. More blocks, more score. Once you start, you will not stop playing this block game.
HOW TO PLAY
- Connecting two blocks with a matching color.
- Drawing a line to link two blocks. Be careful! Make sure the lines won't overlap or cross each other.
- Cover the entire board. Use up every single tile!

FEATURES
• Over 800 free levels
• 6 different board sizes
• Colorful Dots and UI
• Musical Sound Effects
• No Time Limit
